<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="mt-5 row justify-content-center">
  <div class="mt-5 col-12 col-md-8 position-relative text-light">
    <div class="wow fadeInUp card mb-0 bg-dark text-light gl-shadow">
      <h4 class="mt-4 text-center text-white gl-font font-weight-bolder" style="font-size: 40px;text-shadow: 2px 6px 3px #000000;">Joining MMUCraft</h4>
      <div class="card-body p-3">
        <div class="text-center text-white">
          Here is a step by step guide on how to join this private server. Some of the detail might need your attention. Please refer back to here or contact an admin if you encounter any problem.
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="text-white gl-font font-weight-bolder" style="font-size: 20px ;">
          1 - Getting the invitation link
        </h4>
        <div class="mt-3">Smash on this button to get your invitation link:</div>
        <a class="btn btn-light my-3" target="_blank" href="/invite">Get Invitation Here</a>
        <div>You need to provide a valid MMU email address in order to get the invitation link. After pressing the send button, go check your MMU email box. Within a few minutes, you should receive a MMUCraft email. Click on the button provided in the email will open up an account creation page.</div>
      </div>
      <hr>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="text-white gl-font font-weight-bolder" style="font-size: 20px ;">
          2 - Creating an account
        </h4>
        <div class="mt-3">On account creation page, enter your username and password. Finally, press on the create button.</div>
          <div class="text-danger mt-3">The username will use as your in-game username. Not only for login purposes. Moreover, there is no password confirmation input. Make sure you spelled your password correctly. If you make any mistake, please contact admins.</div>
          <div class="mt-3">If you have an existing official Minecraft username, it is recommended to use that name as our private server database is independant which has no connection with official Minecraft server.</div>
      </div>
      <hr>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="text-white gl-font font-weight-bolder" style="font-size: 20px ;">
          3 - Get Minecraft (Skip if you already have it)
        </h4>
        <div class="mt-3">On account creation page, enter your username and password. Finally, press on the create button.</div>
          <div>It is recommended to get Minecraft officially. If you enjoy the game, please consider buying Minecraft to support the developers. Click <a target="_blank" href="https://minecraft.net/">here</a> to get official Minecraft.</div>
          <div class="mt-3">However, if you feel like saving some money, please join our Discord group for more information:</div>
          <a class="btn btn-light mt-3" target="_blank" href="https://discord.gg/jMtqPjH">Our Discord</a>
          <div class="mt-3">Or else, search them yourself. Hope you get what I mean.</div>
      </div>
      <hr>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="text-white gl-font font-weight-bolder" style="font-size: 20px ;">
          4 - Joining the server
        </h4>
        <div>After you get everything installed, start the launcher. Note that you need internet the run the launcher for the first time. Make sure the username is matched as the one you registered and the game version is set to the correct version.</div>
        <div class="mt-3">Run Minecraft and in Multiplayer, click on Direct Connect, enter the following address: <span class="text-info">minecraft.mmu.edu.my</span></div>
        <div class="mt-3">Click connect and you should be able to join the server.</div>
      </div>
      <hr>
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="text-white gl-font font-weight-bolder" style="font-size: 20px ;">
          5 - Login to the server (world) 
        </h4>
          <div>Once you get into the server, you cannot perform any action yet. Press "/" to and enter "/login" into the message box following by a space and your password. It should look something like this:</div>
          <div class="mt-3"><span class="text-info">/login mypassword123</span></div>
          <div class="mt-3">Press enter to execute. If your password is correct, you can now play the game.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>